***************************************************************************************************************



                 Describes tools and other wordlists that are usefull for pentest



***************************************************************************************************************




Feroxbuster : Can be used for subdomain enumeration and directory scanning.

               git clone https://github.com/nirsarkar/feroxbuster.git

SecLists   : A very usefull wordlist with modern injection payloads and many other discovery wordlists.
 			
 				git clone https://github.com/danielmiessler/SecLists.git

HiddenEye  : A Phishing attack tool but can be used for social engenirng.
 
                 git clone https://github.com/Morsmalleo/HiddenEye.git

Burpsuite  : Burpsiute is a application testing software. The class-leading vulnerability scanning, penetration testing, and web app security platform. Burpsuite is pre-installed in 	
				kali linux.
				https://portswigger.net/burp

Nmap       : Nmap ("Network Mapper") is a free and open source utility for network discovery and security auditing.Nmap is pre-installed in kali linux.Nmap contains many usefull 					scripts.

Scripts : There are some publicly available scripts that can be used to find the vulnerabilties inside a server

			Docker : git clone https://github.com/stealthcopter/deepce.git

			Linux machine : https://github.com/carlospolop/PEASS-ng/releases

			Windows machine : https://github.com/carlospolop/PEASS-ng/releases

			